          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "REC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The beam deflected from the cyclotron and",
                "collimated through the shielding walls impinges on",
                "the target T (a foil of polyethylene). The protons,",
                "scattered and recoil, are detected in the stilbene",
                "viewed by a iP21 photomultiplier tube. The beam is",
                "monitored by measuring the ionization produced in a",
                "shallow ionization chamber full of argon which has",
                " (in turn) been calibrated against a faraday cup."
              ]
            }
          ],
