          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The full beam energy using a liquid hydrogen",
                "target. Only the proton at the smaller angle from the",
                "beam was detected (method I). The measurement",
                "proceeded as follows: first, the coincidence counting",
                "rate was determined with T full of air, next with T",
                "full of liquid hydrogen boiling at atmospheric",
                "pressure, and finally the liquid hydrogen was",
                "evaporated and the background redetermined. This",
                "cycle was repeated twice."
              ]
            }
          ],
